** [[File:Silver medal africa.svg|15px]] Runners-up (2): [[1965 African Cup of Nations|1965]], [[1996 African Cup of Nations|1996]]
** [[File:Bronze medal africa.svg|15px]] Third place (1): [[1962 African Cup of Nations|1962]]
